movie.title: Rabbit-Proof Fence
movie.plot: In 1931, three Aboriginal girls escape after being plucked from their homes to be trained as domestic staff, and set off on a trek across the Outback.
movie.awards: Nominated for 1 Golden Globe. Another 23 wins & 24 nominations.
